WITH RankedTitles AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS title_id,
        t.title,
        t.production_year,
        COUNT(k.id) AS keyword_count
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    WHERE 
        t.production_year >= 2000
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year
), 
TitleDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        rt.title_id,
        rt.title,
        rt.production_year,
        rt.keyword_count,
        ak.name AS actor_name,
        COUNT(c.id) AS cast_count
    FROM 
        RankedTitles rt
    LEFT JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON rt.title_id = cc.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        cast_info c ON cc.subject_id = c.person_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        aka_name ak ON c.person_id = ak.person_id
    GROUP BY 
        rt.title_id, rt.title, rt.production_year, rt.keyword_count, ak.name
    ORDER BY 
        rt.keyword_count DESC
),
FinalResults AS (
    SELECT 
        td.title,
        td.production_year,
        td.keyword_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT td.actor_name, ', ') AS actors,
        td.cast_count
    FROM 
        TitleDetails td
    GROUP BY 
        td.title, td.production_year, td.keyword_count, td.cast_count
)
SELECT 
    title,
    production_year,
    keyword_count,
    actors,
    cast_count
FROM 
    FinalResults
WHERE 
    keyword_count > 0
ORDER BY 
    production_year DESC, 
    keyword_count DESC

GROUP BY "t1"."id", "t1"."title", "t1"."production_year") AS "t3" ON "complete_cast"."movie_id" = "t3"."TITLE_ID") AS "t4" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "t4"."subject_id") AS "t5" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "t5"."person_id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "t5"."TITLE_ID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT") AS "t7"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "keyword", "phonetic_code"
FROM "keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("TITLE", "TITLE") AS "TITLE", "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "KEYWORD_COUNT", "ACTORS", "CAST_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "TITLE", "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "KEYWORD_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "ACTOR_NAME", ', ') AS "ACTORS", "CAST_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "t5"."TITLE_ID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "aka_name"."name", MIN("aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", COUNT("t5"."id0") AS "CAST_COUNT"
FROM "aka_name"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT "t4"."TITLE_ID", "t4"."TITLE", "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t4"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "t4"."id", "t4"."movie_id", "t4"."subject_id", "t4"."status_id", "cast_info"."id" AS "id0", "cast_info"."person_id", "cast_info"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "cast_info"."person_role_id", "cast_info"."note", "cast_info"."nr_order", "cast_info"."role_id"
FROM "cast_info"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT "t3"."TITLE_ID", "t3"."TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "complete_cast"."id", "complete_cast"."movie_id", "complete_cast"."subject_id", "complete_cast"."status_id"
FROM "complete_cast"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT MIN("t1"."id") AS "TITLE_ID", "t1"."title" AS "TITLE", "t1"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT("s1"."id") AS "KEYWORD_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "t0"."id", "t0"."movie_id", "t0"."title", "t0"."imdb_index", "t0"."kind_id", "t0"."production_year", "t0"."phonetic_code", "t0"."episode_of_id", "t0"."season_nr", "t0"."episode_nr", "t0"."note", "t0"."md5sum", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id0", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t0" ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "t1"."id", "t1"."title", "t1"."production_year") AS "t3" ON "complete_cast"."movie_id" = "t3"."TITLE_ID") AS "t4" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "t4"."subject_id") AS "t5" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "t5"."person_id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "t5"."TITLE_ID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT") AS "t7"
WHERE "t7"."KEYWORD_COUNT" > 0
GROUP BY "TITLE", "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "KEYWORD_COUNT", "CAST_COUNT"
ORDER BY "PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "KEYWORD_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t12"
